    <div class="row-fluid cool-font">

        <h3>SuiMo -> (Suica x Passmo) + BitCoin</h3>
        <p>Got Bitcoins?  Traveling to Japan? Hate carrying cash?  We can help </p>
        <p><a href="/info" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid section1">
        <div class="span12 cool-font">
            <div class="span3">
                <img class="displayed" id="btcimage" src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/8869944/suimo/btc.jpg"/>
                <h3 class="text-center"> pay by bitcoins </h3>
                <p>Visit bitstamp.com or mtgox.com to get bitcoins in your wallet.  Pay us in bitcoin and we will send you a Japanese
                e-cash card pre-charged with Yen.  Kind of like a debit card ... </p>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
                <img class="displayed" id="suicapassmo" src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/8869944/suimo/suicapassmo.jpg" width="50%" height="50%" />
                <h3 class="text-center">we send you card</h3>
                <p>We ship you the card before you leave.  Please allow time for delivery.  Usually about 2 weeks if sent internationally.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
                <img class="displayed" src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/8869944/suimo/wallet.jpg"/>
                <h3 class="text-center">use card</h3>
                <p>Use the cash card in over thousands of convenience stores, pay for busses, trains, rail station shops, and beyond
                    ... there is not enough room on the website to list all the stores that take Suica or Passmo.  You must discover for yourself.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="span3">
                <img class="displayed" src="https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/8869944/suimo/back.jpg"/>
                <h3 class="text-center">get remainder</h3>
                <p>Done using Suica or Passmo?  Have a left-over balance?  Just send us the card back, and we will refund your balance in
                    Bitcoins. What else can you wish for?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
